* Introduce 'translate into the taget language' questions:
PropositionBuilder has extra method askTranslateToTarget(), 
triggered each time by a checkbox in craft lesson. This will add a new 
attribute to the proposition json, that will get added to the proposition, 
and will be considered every time a new proposition is displayed to the user.


